# Chins North — Clean Air Solutions App
## Claude Code Build Prompt

---

## Business Overview

**Business:** CHINS NORTH™ — Clean Air Solutions
**Location:** Greater Houston, TX
**Contact:** +1 (281) 687-7575
**TikTok:** @chinsnorth7
**Tagline:** *"Clean air is an investment, not a luxury."*

**Services:**
- Full air duct cleaning (supply & return)
- HVAC unit cleaning & upkeep
- Mold inspection & treatment (visual / non-invasive)
- Dryer vent cleaning
- Preventative maintenance services
- FREE system inspection with every full air duct cleaning
- Optional HVAC anti-microbial sanitation & deodorization (complimentary with full service)

**Brand Colors:**
- Primary green: `#2D6A4F` (dark forest green, from logo)
- Accent green: `#52B788` (mid green)
- White: `#FFFFFF`
- Off-white background: `#F8F9FA`
