## Tech Stack

- **Framework:** Next.js 15 App Router
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- **Language:** TypeScript
- **Package manager:** pnpm
- **Icons:** lucide-react
- **Design Skill:** v0-ui (load `/mnt/skills/user/v0-ui/SKILL.md` before writing any JSX)

---

## Pages & Routes

### `/` — Landing Page (Home)
Hero section with:
- CHINS NORTH logo (text-based, styled with brand colors)
- Headline: "Breathe Cleaner Air. Live Better."
- Subheadline: "Professional duct cleaning, mold remediation & HVAC upkeep for Greater Houston homes."
- Two CTAs: **"Book a Free Inspection"** (primary green button) + **"Call Now: (281) 687-7575"** (outlined)
- Trust badges: "Licensed Technicians", "HVAC Code Compliant", "Greater Houston Serving"

Services section:
- 6 service cards with lucide-react icons, green accent, short 1-line descriptions
- FREE inspection callout banner (green background, white text)

Why Choose Us section:
- 3 points with checkmark icons:
  - Highly knowledgeable technicians with extensive field experience
  - Work performed in line with HVAC code standards and best practices
  - Focused on proper airflow, cleanliness, and long-term system health

Approach section:
- 3-step visual: Inspect → Identify → Improve
- Brief copy under each step

Testimonials section (static, 3 cards — placeholder names, Houston-area, 5-star)

CTA footer banner: "Ready for cleaner air?" + Book button

### `/services` — Services Detail Page
Full breakdown of each service with:
- Icon + title + description (2–3 sentences each)
- "What's included" bullet list per service
- Pricing note: "Contact us for a free quote"
- CTA per card: "Schedule This Service"

### `/booking` — Booking / Contact Form
Fields:
- Full Name
- Phone Number
- Email
- Address (Street, City, ZIP)
- Service Type (dropdown: Air Duct Cleaning, HVAC Upkeep, Mold Inspection, Dryer Vent, Preventative Maintenance, Not Sure)
- Preferred Date (date picker)
- Preferred Time (Morning / Afternoon / Evening toggle)
- Message / Notes (optional textarea)
- Submit button: "Request Free Inspection"

On submit: show success state ("We'll call you within 24 hours to confirm your appointment.")
Form validation: all required fields, phone format check.
No backend needed — use a `mailto:` or `formspree` action for MVP, or leave a `// TODO: connect to backend` comment.

### `/about` — About Page
- Company mission paragraph
- "Our Approach" section (Inspection-first, system-focused)
- Goal statement: "Our goal is to improve life quality from within the property through preventive maintenance of your HVAC system."
- Photo placeholder section (use clean placeholder images — no blobs)
- Contact info card

### `/faq` — FAQ Page
Pre-populate with 8–10 relevant Q&As, e.g.:
- How often should I clean my air ducts?
- What's included in the free inspection?
- Do you service commercial properties?
- How long does a full duct cleaning take?
- Is mold remediation safe for my family?
- What areas do you serve?
- How is CHINS NORTH different from competitors?
- Do I need to be home during service?

Use shadcn `Accordion` component for collapse/expand.

---

## Global Components

### `<Header />`
- CHINS NORTH logo (left)
- Nav links: Home, Services, FAQ, About, Book Now
- Mobile: hamburger menu (Sheet component from shadcn)
- Sticky on scroll, white background, subtle shadow

### `<Footer />`
- Logo + tagline
- Quick links
- Contact: phone + "Serving Greater Houston"
- Copyright line

### `<BookingCTA />` — Reusable floating/inline CTA
Used at bottom of every page. Green background, white text, phone number + Book button.

---

## Design Rules (from v0-ui skill)

- Mobile-first, min 16px text inputs, min 44px touch targets
- No gradient blobs — use clean white/green sections with real spacing
- Semantic HTML: `<main>`, `<header>`, `<nav>`, `<section>`
- Consistent icons: 20px or 24px lucide-react only
- Split into focused components — never one giant `page.tsx`
- Green (#2D6A4F) for primary actions, light green tints for backgrounds
- Typography: clean sans-serif, bold headings, readable body

---

## File Structure

```
app/
  layout.tsx
  page.tsx                  ← Home
  services/page.tsx
  booking/page.tsx
  about/page.tsx
  faq/page.tsx
components/
  Header.tsx
  Footer.tsx
  BookingCTA.tsx
  ServiceCard.tsx
  TestimonialCard.tsx
  BookingForm.tsx
  HeroSection.tsx
  ApproachSteps.tsx
  WhyChooseUs.tsx
  FaqAccordion.tsx
public/
  logo.svg (or text-based component)
```

---

## Implementation Order

1. Read `/mnt/skills/user/v0-ui/SKILL.md` first
2. Scaffold Next.js project with pnpm + shadcn init
3. Build `Header` + `Footer` components
4. Build Home page (`/`) — this is the most important page
5. Build `BookingForm` + `/booking` page
6. Build `/services` page
7. Build `/faq` page with Accordion
8. Build `/about` page
9. Wire `BookingCTA` into all pages
10. Final pass: mobile responsiveness check on all pages

---

## Notes

- This is an MVP — no auth, no dashboard, no CMS needed
- Keep it fast: minimal JS, no heavy animations
- The booking form doesn't need a live backend — `formspree` or mailto fallback is fine
- Do not install unnecessary deps — shadcn + lucide + tailwind covers everything
- Brand voice: professional, trustworthy, Houston-local, health-focused
